snippet.textDisplay: It's quite intriguing how this song showcases a captivating paradox. On one hand, it warns about the curse of lavish feasts, but on the other hand, the performers, dressed in mesmerizing Mahrin attire, unintentionally promote the very extravagance they caution against. It's ironic how their actions contradict their message, and it makes me think about the complexities and contradictions that exist in our society.

snippet.textDisplay:
The inner folds of this song bears the emotional message. Reflects the things which makes us know the ''essence of girl'', Her teary journey from one house to another,  then adopting the new style of survival , dealing with the new faces ,new intents etc etc and also the marriage expenses burden on the shoulders of her father , The  dowry menace...
Hope every daughter of the world meets the cooperative, compassionate and lovely families where they gets married.
